(<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">OMB</ENAMEX>). <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">OMB</ENAMEX> provided guidance on the preparation and submission of
strategic plans as a new part of its <ENAMEX TYPE="PRODUCT">Circular No. A-11</ENAMEX>-the basic
