<TIMEX TYPE="DATE">fiscal year</TIMEX> (copies are to be provided to other congressional
<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">committees</ENAMEX> and to the public upon request). The <NUMEX TYPE="ORDINAL">first</NUMEX> of these
